Title: The List
Plot: Nobody takes much notice when a death row inmate vows on the electric chair to come back from the dead and kill five men who have wronged him during his time in prison, until a guard is mysteriously murdered in the former inmate's cell.
GuestStars: Bokeem Woodbine, Greg Rogers, Mitchell Kosterman, Paul Raskin, Denny Arnold, Craig Brunanski, Joseph Patrick Finn, Bruce Pinard, Don MacKay, Badja Djola, John Toles-Bey, Ken Foree, April Grace, J.T. Walsh
